name: QB's Journey V1.1.0
description:
Play as QB, a small cube with one eye as you maneuver your way through strange places such as a field, a cave and a forest! This DEMO contains level 1, and some updated visuals and MUSIC. So yeah, THIS GAME ISN'T FINISHED YET!!!

THERE WILL BE BUGS, MOST LIKELY NEAR THE END OF THE GAME!!!
